i agree that all those things Kendrik said were done for us, but when you look at the real use of them, rogues barely use one quarter of them. you can always make a huge list of enhancement, taking all the fixes of what was broken in the past, and it's good it was done, but it doesn't mean it's enough, nor that nothing else should/could be done...<br>
